      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Exhibiting consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a refined driving experience that exceeds standard expectations for its class. We invite you to experience this exceptional balance of performance and sophistication firsthand.",
      "price": 34800.0,
